<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.8">
<l>muḻutiv vaiyakam muṟaikeṭa maṟaitalum muṉivaṉum muṉiveyta</l>
<l>maḻuvi ṉālmaṉṉa rāruyir vavviya maintaṉum vārāṉāl</l>
<l>oḻuku nuṇpaṉik koṭuṅkiya pēṭaiyai yaṭaṅkavañ ciṟaikōlit</l>
<l>taḻuvu naḷḷiruḷ taṉimaiyiṟ kaṭiyatōr koṭuviṉai yaṟiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who swept away with his axe the dear lives of the kings</l>
<l rend="indent">as soon as the entire world order vanished</l>
<l>When it decayed, so that the great muni’s rage arose,</l>
<l rend="indent">does not come [here] at all!</l>
<l>I do not know of a harsher fate than the cruelty of loneliness at midnight</l>
<l rend="indent">when, as a hen which shrinks from the fine dripping rain</l>
<l>Crouches down, [her mate’s] beautiful wings enfold and embrace [her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
